column4: NSLOCTEXT("[07B985964D91CAD70D9B2BB87BBF9B15]", "6D1B34474F1A2F406BF7B89317422707", "I heard from Jiji that {Partner} will digivolve.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07B985964D91CAD70D9B2BB87BBF9B15]", "877C7F824A087363ADEB74B86FE2D62D", "From Fresh Digimon to In-Training Digimon, it only takes six hours.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07B985964D91CAD70D9B2BB87BBF9B15]", "CE763D0F46832881A295E79E01DDB22B", "From there to Rookie, it takes about a day to digivolve.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07B985964D91CAD70D9B2BB87BBF9B15]", "90C4BCBD444A2F23407812BD5722D27A", "Then to the next Champion Digimon, it takes about three days to digivolve.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07B985964D91CAD70D9B2BB87BBF9B15]", "EF1B390B45579DAA750AD9A93E3B6DD8", "And what was the next generation? I forgot, but there\'s more.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07B985964D91CAD70D9B2BB87BBF9B15]", "307A3C5B43716214EC8E9F86B8510DB2", "Digivolution is related to weight, parameters, and care mistakes.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07B985964D91CAD70D9B2BB87BBF9B15]", "089E4CCF4F8467CCB573B19FD4EA2E0D", "I don\'t understand very well. I\'ll ask Jiji next chance.")
